headline.main: Quake of 6.5 Magnitude Strikes Off Papua New Guinea
headline.print_headline: Quake of 6.5 Magnitude Strikes Off Papua New Guinea

lead_paragraph: An earthquake of 6.5 magnitude struck off the south coast of Papua New Guinea on Monday, the U.S. Geological Survey (USGS) said.
